{"tid":1887770,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好掛住前度男朋友。。。","createTime":"2020-02-19T18:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T00:32:59.000Z","uid":247416,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ef817dec6182794d81309df1302f6ef0749368f3","tid":1887770,"uid":247416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T18:59:19.000Z","msg":"同前度男朋友分開左就快大半年<br />\n但我地一齊左五年半。<br />\n雙方唔係因為淡左唔係因為有第三者分開<br />\n而係男方嘅屋企好大負擔<br />\n佢覺得兼顧唔到咁多野而被迫分開<br />\n佢覺得再同我一齊都俾唔到乜野承諾我 <br />\n所以就決定分手<br />\n我同佢講我可以等可以陪佢一齊面對<br />\n但佢就好決絕咁推開我 <br />\n唔覆wts唔聽電話唔俾我揾到佢。<br />\n我抱住為左佢好為左佢可以安靜咁面對屋企嘅野<br />\n我只好唔再揾佢唔煩住佢<br />\n到依家都仲每日都會諗住佢<br />\n成日發夢見到佢<br />\n成日喊到收唔到 嗰陣先知有失戀創傷後遺症<br />\n去左睇心理醫生 好返少少 依家又再係咁了<br />\n我好掛住佢。。我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3897200016122a469a7a17f055cc12005613b2c","tid":1887770,"uid":308751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T19:03:18.000Z","msg":"有冇共同朋友?<br />\n叫佢哋幫你問下佢仲有冇掛住你<br />\n如果有就叫啲friend講下你而家嘅狀況<br />\n或者佢會回心轉意呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513d5b129399dc0f1dded1a81ae85cd437d38fd8","tid":1887770,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T19:03:25.000Z","msg":"當香港人仲掛住排口罩 搶廁紙 討論邊個邊個ig女神<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1887691\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1887691</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手推thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fb53fa5a617b8176abb8492c43455d97529784","tid":1887770,"uid":90483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T19:24:18.000Z","msg":"我分左兩年幾都好掛住